title: The Anthony Cumia Show 2014-09-17
description:
Wednesday, September 17, 2014

A drowsy Ant begins by talking about the iOS 8, John Kerry getting heckled, a case of unsolicited sex, and then admits that in his dreams he is the "rapiest." A caller triggers Anthony to rant about moles and Dr. Steve calls to explain why one region can be "molier" than the other. Max Koch also calls in to talk Sopranos, oral sex, kleptomania, movies, and keeping your sack fresh. Ant reads a few submissions from people who would like to take part in the new "unblock promotion," addresses the myth that he wakes up late, we watch the music video "Call the Cops," check out an unreal video from a school, and then we are treated to a few more gems from the callers.
